OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FThe inquests into the deaths of two
OL,7,Fmen killed in the Manchester synagogue
OL,8,Fattack are set to take place in spring
OL,9,F2027.
OL,11,FMelvin Cravitz, 66, died along with
OL,12,FAdrian Daulby, 53, when Jihad Al-
OL,13,FShamie targeted the Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,14,FSynagogue in Crumpsall, on 2 October.
OL,16,FMr Daulby was struck by a single
OL,17,Fgunshot wound to the chest fired by an
OL,18,Farmed police officer as he and other
OL,19,Fworshippers held the main door of the
OL,20,Fsynagogue shut when Al-Shamie, 35,
OL,21,Ftried to force his way inside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
