FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FA pre-inquest review hearing on
OL,7,FThursday 26 February heard that attack
OL,8,Fsurvivor Yoni Finlay was seriously
OL,9,Finjured by the same bullet that passed
OL,10,Fthrough the door and took Mr Daulby's
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FMr Cravitz died from multiple knife
OL,14,Fwounds inflicted by Al-Shamie, and
OL,15,Fthree other people were injured, as
OL,16,Fpeople gathered to mark the holy day
OL,17,Fof Yom Kippur, the holiest day of the
OL,18,Fyear for Jews.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
