OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FA pre-inquest review hearing for Al-
OL,7,FShamie will be held at Manchester
OL,8,FCoroner's Court on Friday 27 February.
OL,10,FThe Syrian-born UK citizen began his
OL,11,Frampage by driving his Kia Picanto car
OL,12,Fat security staff and the external
OL,13,Fgates of the synagogue.
OL,15,FHe died from multiple gunshot wounds
OL,16,Fafter he ran towards armed police
OL,17,F"aggressively" while carrying a knife
OL,18,Fand wearing what appeared to be a
OL,19,Fsuicide belt.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FLawyers for Mr Finlay and fellow
OL,7,Fsurvivor Andrew Franks, who was
OL,8,Fstabbed in the incident, want them to
OL,9,Fbe given Interested Persons (IP)
OL,10,Fstatus for the proceedings, which
OL,11,Fwould enable them to examine witnesses
OL,12,Fand receive disclosure of relevant
OL,13,Fstatements and documents.
OL,15,FAnthony Metzer KC, representing Mr
OL,16,FFinlay, told Manchester Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt: "He is not simply a survivor of
OL,18,Fthis terrorist atrocity. He is in a
OL,19,Fvery special category, given the
OL,20,Fextraordinary circumstances which
OL,21,Fresulted in his injuries."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FAn application for IP status has also
OL,7,Fbeen made on behalf of Ellis Franks,
OL,8,Fwho gave first aid to his son and
OL,9,Fremained with him until the emergency
OL,10,Fservices arrived.
OL,12,FChris Daw KC, representing Andrew and
OL,13,FEllis Franks, said: "This incident was
OL,14,Fan attack on the entire Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,17,F"We suggest the law has taken a wrong
OL,18,Fturn in excluding survivors... they
OL,19,Fshould not have been historically
OL,20,Fexcluded at either inquests or
OL,21,Finquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,F"This is the case in which the
OL,7,Fprinciple needs to be revisited."
OL,9,FHe said Andrew Franks sustained "life-
OL,10,Fchanging and almost fatal injuries"
OL,11,Fand was "at the heart of the events."
OL,13,FJudge Alexia Durran, the chief coroner
OL,14,Fof England and Wales, presiding over
OL,15,Fthe hearing, said she intended to rule
OL,16,Fon the applications at a further pre-
OL,17,Finquest hearing on 3 September.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
