OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FA jury will hear the joint inquests in
OL,7,F2027, examining the radicalisation of
OL,8,FAl-Shamie and whether the attack could
OL,9,Fhave been prevented.
OL,11,FThree parallel proceedings have yet to
OL,12,Fbe resolved, the court heard.
OL,14,FAn investigation by the Independent
OL,15,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) into
OL,16,Fthe actions of Greater Manchester
OL,17,FPolice (GMP) armed officers at the
OL,18,Fscene is due to conclude this spring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
