OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772132672
OL,3,CInquests into Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattack deaths to take place next year
OL,6,FA separate IOPC investigation into
OL,7,FGMP's prior contact or knowledge of Al-
OL,8,FShamie is scheduled to report back in
OL,9,Fthe autumn.
OL,11,FMohammad Bashir, 31, an alleged
OL,12,Fassociate of Al-Shamie, is set to go
OL,13,Fon trial at Manchester Crown Court in
OL,14,FJuly accused of preparation of
OL,15,Fterrorist acts and disseminating
OL,16,Fterrorist publications.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
